Name: Average time it takes the Completed + Closed to be done
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Closed and the end of the case

Name: Total time from Accepted + In Progress to Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total resolution time of Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Closed and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time between Accepted + In Progress and Completed + Closed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total waiting time to the Completed + Closed
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total time it takes Completed + Closed after the execution of Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Closed'
